text.tspan: Each submarine can adjust its buoyancy to settle beneath the surface of any liquid layer.
In the same way, the buoyancy of torpedoes must be chosen to target the infidels.
For honour, torpedoes fire simultaneously on a timer.
In the year 3020, humanity has come a long way but religious war continues. Years of technological
innovation have left the oceans full of polluting liquids, which have settled into different layers.
